w=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span> of the disk in Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> and Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, respectively?</p>\n",
